author: PostmodernJukebox
description:
“Hotel California” by Eagles Vintage Havana style cover by Postmodern Jukebox ft. Rogelio Douglas, Jr.
PMJ World Tour Tix: http://pmjtour.com | Get the song: http://www.pmjlive.com/hotelcalifornia
Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPMJ | PMJ on Spotify: http://pmjlive.com/pmjspotify 

If you’ve seen him live, you already know that emcee Rogelio Douglas, Jr. is truly a showstopper - now, he’s back with his 4th PMJ video! This time, we’re taking the Eagles’ 1977 classic, “Hotel California” back to Havana’s El Tropicana, complete with Afro-Cuban percussion by Giovanni Rodriguez, drums by Petar Janjic, and a Sunny Holiday Salsa cameo. ¡Bienvenidos al Hotel California!
